show.title: The Boy Who Beat The Board
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/XCLK9B
show.description: When chess grandmaster Mukesh Tandon dies tragically in a plane crash, his soul awakens in the body of a 13-year-old boy, Mukul. As he navigates a second life, Mukul reunites with his grieving wife Juhi, battles rival prodigies like Vikram and Zakir, and faces dark conspiracies from Kiara and King. With unmatched strategy and an unbreakable will, Mukul fights to reclaim his legacy and protect Juhi, proving that genius and love can transcend even death. Watch Now!
